# 🧠 First — Understand the Rule

AXI ordering rules:

✔ Same ID → must complete in order
✔ Different IDs → may complete out-of-order

Example:

Master issues:

```
AR ID=0  (Address A)
AR ID=1  (Address B)
```

Slave is allowed to respond:

```
RID=1  (Address B first)
RID=0  (Address A later)
```

That is legal AXI.

